site ID (data from the same site have similar environmental conditions and are recognized as the same site by data source. One site can have multiple plots)

Profile ID (Data of different layer but represent same soil profile have the same profile ID)

column7: Carbon variables measured across time must be consistent. For example, measurements of TC in 2004 and SOC in 2012 can't be in one time series. SOC and SOM means concentration, "stock" denotes SOC or SOM stock.
